        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This staff is topped with carved animal and monster heads. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Nature checks to identify animals.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Know Direction]{Know Direction}</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Magic Fang]{Magic Fang}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Summon Animal]{Summon Animal}</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Animal Messenger]{Animal Messenger}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Speak with Animals]{Speak with Animals}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Summon Animal]{Summon Animal}</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Animal Form]{Animal Form}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Summon Animal]{Summon Animal}</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Summon Animal]{Summon Animal}</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Animal Form]{Animal Form}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Moon Frenzy]{Moon Frenzy}</em> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Summon Animal]{Summon Animal}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
